---
// src/components/SecClients.astro
---
<section class="sec s6" id="sec5">
  <div class="s6-inner">

    <div class="s6-header">
      <span class="s6-eyebrow fade-up">Procurement</span>
      <h2 class="s6-title fade-up fade-up-d1">조달청 등록제품</h2>
      <p class="s6-sub fade-up fade-up-d2">이담에스티의 제품은 조달청에 공식 등록되어 공공기관 납품이 가능합니다</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s6-grid">

      <!-- 미디어박스 -->
      <a class="s6-card fade-up fade-up-d1" href="/products/mediabox">
        <div class="s6-thumb">
          <img src="/images/products/mediabox-01.jpg" alt="mediabox" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="s6-thumb-ov">
            <span class="s6-thumb-cta">자세히 보기 →</span>
          </div>
          <div class="s6-card-badge">등록완료</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s6-card-body">
          <h3 class="s6-card-title">미디어박스</h3>
          <p class="s6-card-desc">HDTV 동시녹화 녹화영상 키워드 검색 및 편집 시스템</p>
          <div class="s6-card-tags">
            <span class="s6-tag">방송 모니터링</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">실시간 분석</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">특허 보유</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 컴퓨터 서버 -->
      <a class="s6-card fade-up fade-up-d2" href="/products/server">
        <div class="s6-thumb">
          <img src="/images/products/server.jpg" alt="컴퓨터 서버" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="s6-thumb-ov">
            <span class="s6-thumb-cta">자세히 보기 →</span>
          </div>
          <div class="s6-card-badge">등록완료</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s6-card-body">
          <h3 class="s6-card-title">컴퓨터 서버</h3>
          <p class="s6-card-desc">방송·미디어 환경에 최적화된 고성능 서버. 안정적인 24/7 운용을 보장합니다.</p>
          <div class="s6-card-tags">
            <span class="s6-tag">고성능</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">24/7 운용</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">직접생산</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 디스크 어레이 -->
      <a class="s6-card fade-up fade-up-d3" href="/products/disk-array">
        <div class="s6-thumb">
          <img src="/images/products/disk-array-nas4036.jpg" alt="디스크 어레이" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="s6-thumb-ov">
            <span class="s6-thumb-cta">자세히 보기 →</span>
          </div>
          <div class="s6-card-badge">등록완료</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s6-card-body">
          <h3 class="s6-card-title">디스크 어레이</h3>
          <p class="s6-card-desc">대용량 미디어 스토리지 솔루션. SAN·NAS 기반의 고속 데이터 접근을 제공합니다.</p>
          <div class="s6-card-tags">
            <span class="s6-tag">SAN·NAS</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">대용량</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">고속 접근</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- LED 전광판 -->
      <a class="s6-card fade-up fade-up-d4" href="/products/led">
        <div class="s6-thumb">
          <img src="/images/products/led.jpg" alt="LED 전광판" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="s6-thumb-ov">
            <span class="s6-thumb-cta">자세히 보기 →</span>
          </div>
          <div class="s6-card-badge">등록완료</div>
        </div>
        <div class="s6-card-body">
          <h3 class="s6-card-title">LED 전광판</h3>
          <p class="s6-card-desc">실내외 대형 LED 디스플레이. P1.5 초고해상도부터 대형 전광판까지 맞춤 설계합니다.</p>
          <div class="s6-card-tags">
            <span class="s6-tag">P1.5 고해상도</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">실내외</span>
            <span class="s6-tag">맞춤 설계</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="s6-notice fade-up">
      <div class="s6-notice-icon">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
          <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="9" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <path d="M10 9v5M10 6.5v.5" stroke="#1a2f8a" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p>이담에스티의 모든 등록제품은 조달청 나라장터를 통해 공공기관 직접 구매가 가능합니다. 자세한 사항은 <strong onclick="document.getElementById('sec7').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">문의하기</strong>를 통해 확인하세요.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s6 { background: #f4f6f9; }
  .s6-inner { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 48px; }

  /* 헤더 */
  .s6-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .s6-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #1a2f8a; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .s6-eyebrow::before, .s6-eyebrow::after {
    content: ''; display: block; width: 20px; height: 2px; background: #1a2f8a;
  }
  .s6-title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 48px); font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em; color: #0D1F2D; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .s6-sub { font-size: 15px; color: #888; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* 카드 그리드 */
  .s6-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  /* 카드 — a 태그 */
  .s6-card {
    background: #fff; border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #eaecef;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }
  .s6-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(26,47,138,0.13);
    transform: translateY(-6px);
  }

  /* 썸네일 */
  .s6-thumb {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    background: #e8edf4;
  }
  .s6-thumb img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.45s;
  }
  .s6-card:hover .s6-thumb img { transform: scale(1.05); }

  /* 호버 오버레이 */
  .s6-thumb-ov {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(26,47,138,0);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .s6-card:hover .s6-thumb-ov { background: rgba(26,47,138,0.55); }
  .s6-thumb-cta {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px);
    transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .s6-card:hover .s6-thumb-cta { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* 뱃지 */
  .s6-card-badge {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #1a2f8a;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  /* 카드 바디 */
  .s6-card-body {
    padding: 20px 22px 24px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
  }
  .s6-card-title {
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800;
    color: #0D1F2D; letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .s6-card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.75; }
  .s6-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .s6-tag {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; color: #777;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .s6-card:hover .s6-tag { border-color: #1a2f8a; color: #1a2f8a; }

  /* 하단 안내 */
  .s6-notice {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
    background: rgba(26,47,138,0.06); border-left: 4px solid #1a2f8a;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 20px 24px;
  }
  .s6-notice-icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .s6-notice p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; }
  .s6-notice strong { color: #1a2f8a; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }

  /* 반응형 */
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .s6-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .s6-inner { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .s6-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
